usha kiran ( 22 april 1929 – 9 march 2000 ) was a hindi and marathi film actress . in a career spanning over four decades she acted in over 50 hindi and marathi films , notably daag ( 1952 ) , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( 1953 ) , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( 1954 ) , chupke chupke ( 1975 ) , mili ( 1975 ) and bawarchi ( 1972 ) . she was also the sheriff of mumbai during 1996 – 97 .